Project Apparel Price Optimization¶

Objective: The main idea behind this problem is the following question: As manager of a company/store, how much should I charge in order to maximize my revenue or profit? Obviously, the answer isnt as high as possible. If you charge one hundred dollars, probably only one or two people will accept to buy it. Although the profit per product is very high, you probably wont even your fixed costs. Charge a very small is also not the best call.
